snippet.title: Overwatch 2 Seasonal Event | Halloween Terror 2022
snippet.description:
LET’S GET SPOOKY 👻

Earn creepy cosmetics, complete spine-tingling co-op missions, and experience the next chapter in the Junkenstein’s Revenge saga! Overwatch 2  Halloween Terror begins Oct 25 - Nov 8!

Learn more about Halloween Terror https://overwatch.blizzard.com/news/23865971/
